@NODE "Einf" "Introduction"
@TOC "MAIN"

@{i}PatchHidden @{ui} is a small Patch, which prevents access to hidden Files.
A file which is protected by "protect <filename> +h", is unaccessable neither
from WB nor from Cli or FileRequester.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Install" "Installation"
@TOC "MAIN"

To Install: Copy @{i}PatchHidden @{ui} into the WBStartup drawer of your Workbench
@{i}PatchHidden @{ui} will be started every time you boot your computer.
You also may copy PatchHidden into your C: drawer, and add the following line
to your user-startup or startup-sequence:

C:PatchHidden >NIL:

@ENDNODE
@NODE "Vor" "System requirements"
@TOC "MAIN"

 · OS 3.0 (v39) +

@ENDNODE
@NODE "Kompak" "Compatibility"
@TOC "MAIN"

@{i}PatchHidden @{ui} works with the Workbench, Cli (KingCON),
ReqTools-FileRequesters etc...

It does not work with ASL-Req! Please use ReqChange!

Incompatibilities? Bugs? Suggestions? Drop @{"us" LINK "Adresse"} a few lines!

@ENDNODE
